# Quick actions and time context

Phase resolution, action visibility, save-row keys, and related constants are documented in **`docs/quick-actions.md`**.

When changing `getQuickActionsPhaseFromSharedContext`, `getSharedAppTimeContext`, `inferSharedSleepContextPhase`, `shouldShowDynamicSleepNavPhase`, or `QUICK_ACTIONS_BY_PHASE`, update that doc and the **Phase and row constants** table if any numbers or order of checks change.
